name: Column Rocket
description:
Can you make your rocket ship through the Columns of Doom? Fast paced physics game where you have to fly your rocket ship around and through columns.

This game is just a prototype, but would love to see what people think. Feedback is always recommended.

NOTE: The Mac and Linux downloadables, I'm unsure if they work. It was my first attempt at making my game(s) available other then Windows or WebGL.
